本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:林怡芬研究生(外文):Yi-fen Lin論文名稱:《四庫全書》的《詩經》學觀點研究論文名稱(外文):A Study of the Academic Point of View of "The Book of Songs" in "Si Ku Quan Shu"指導教授:林葉連指導教授(外文):Ye-lian Lin學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立雲林科技大學系所名稱:漢學資料整理研究所碩士班學門:人文學門學類:中國語文學類論文出版年:2009畢業學年度:97語文別:中文論文頁數:242中文關鍵詞:經學、詩序、詩經、四庫全書、淫詩外文關鍵詞:Sex poems、The Preface to the Book of Songs、study of Confucian、The Book of Songs、Si Ku Quan Shu相關次數:

被引用:5點閱:417評分:下載:139書目收藏:1



《四庫全書》的研究者多半從《四庫全書總目》研究其學術觀點，較少能從實際的著錄探討之，因此本文嘗試從《四庫全書》所著錄的書籍概況、四庫館臣所作的考證，來探討《四庫全書》的《詩經》學觀點。本文共分六章。第一章緒論，說明研究動機與目的外，並限定研究範圍、回顧前人的研究成果，以及簡述各章節的內容。第二章探討《詩經》學爭議問題，以作為探究《詩》學觀點的前提。第三章探討《四庫全書》之編修背景，得出：「尊經崇儒、崇孔尊朱」、「重視《詩》教」、「重漢學考據」、「重視《詩經》的古音韻」、「保留三家《詩》學觀點」等《詩》學觀點。第四章探究《四庫全書總目》經部詩類的《詩》學觀，得出：「推崇《詩序》」、「認為《詩經》是政治美刺詩」、「《詩》有淫詩，用以刺淫，非淫者自述其狀」等《詩》學觀點。第五章從《毛詩註疏》的考證捲中探究《四庫全書》著錄的《詩經》學觀點，得出：「重漢學，兼採宋學」、「不盲從《詩序》」、「反對淫詩說」、「認同美詩，對於刺詩持保留態度」等《詩》學觀點。第六章結論，總結本論文。從以上三方面考察所得，大致符合向來我們認定的四庫館是漢學的大本營，《四庫全書》的學術立場是傾向漢學的，但是我們也發現《四庫全書》對於宋學的接受與認同。館臣雖是漢學派的追隨者，其編纂《四庫全書》用的也是漢學派的方法，但是卻不為門戶所侷限，拘泥於一家之說，反而能破除門戶之見，廣博採納各家之言，使《四庫全書》的內容更臻完備，這種學術立場是值得推崇的。

"Si Ku Quan Shu" Most of the researchers from the "Sikuquanshuzongmu" study the academic point of view, are not removed from the actual description of study, this paper attempts from the "Si Ku Quan Shu" Overview of the book description, Four Hill Museum of the research, to explore the "Si Ku Quan Shu" and "The Book of Songs" point of view.This article is divided into six chapters. Introduction Chapter motivation and purpose of the research studies, but also limit the scope of the study reviewed previous research results, as well as on the contents of the chapters. Chapter II of "The Book of Songs" learning issues, as to explore, "poem" point of view of the premise. Chapter III of "Si Ku Quan Shu" come to the editing context of "respect by the Chung-Ju, Chong Zhu Zun-hole", "great importance" poem "Education", "re-examination, according to Chinese", "attention to" The Book of Songs "ancient music", "retain the three," poem "point" such as "Poem" point of view. Chapter IV Research "Sikuquanshuzongmu" category by the Ministry of poetry, "Poems" concept come to school, "promoted the idea that" poetry sequence "," "believes," The Book of Songs "is the United States and barbed political poetry", "" Poems "have sex Poems for the gill sex, non-sex persons of their own words like "such as" Poem "point of view. Chapter V of " Mao Shi Chu Shu " volume of research into "Si Ku Quan Shu" description of "The Book of Songs" point of view come to the "Chinese, can be either a provident Song" and "blindly" poem sequence, "", "No sex poems to say "," U.S. recognition of poetry and poems for the Spurs have reservations about "such as" Poem "point of view. Chapter VI summarize the conclusions of this paper.From the facts obtained in these three aspects, in line with that of the Four has always been our Museum is the home base of Sinology, "Si Ku Quan Shu" is the tendency of the academic position of the Chinese, but we also found that "Si Ku Quan Shu" Song for the acceptance and recognition . Museum Hill School Although the followers of the Han, the compilation of "Si Ku Quan Shu" is also used in Chinese school, but not limited to a gateway, said a rigidly adhere to, but to get rid of school, broad adoption of each of to make the "Si Ku Quan Shu" better complete content, academic position that merits commendation.

